@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iqgeyh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((v1 - tmp))
    v1 = v1
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.37)) * 0.92)
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.69 * v1 + 0.54)) + (v2 * 0.03))
    v2 = (wp.cos(v1) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.35) + 0.32))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.70) * v2) - wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.39)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(v1) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.09) - (v1 + 0.70 - v2 + 0.12)))
    data[tid] = v0
